Description:
   Tribunal's Hand is a high-level Cleric offensive spell that invokes the
   full authority of Disk's divine tribunal. The Cleric channels the
   combined judgment of the celestial court, delivering a devastating
   critical blow of divine force. The spell calls down Disk's hand as an
   instrument of the tribunal's decision, crushing the target with the
   weight of divine verdict.

   Tribunal's Hand is one of the Cleric's most powerful single-target
   offensive spells, dealing major holy damage. The tribunal aspect means
   the spell has an enhanced critical chance — when the tribunal's decision
   is delivered with full certainty, the blow lands with devastating force.
   It is the culmination of the Cleric's role as an executor of divine
   judgment rather than merely a healer.
